*.zip
public-archivedwl-*.zip
public-archivedwl-*/

# Installers, signing material, and generated native caches
**/*.apk
**/*.aab
**/*.ipa
**/*.jks
**/*.keystore
!**/debug.keystore
**/.cxx/
geo-cache/
tmp/
work/

